Title: The Colossos of Rhodes, vintage artwork by Louis de Caullery, Poster Print
Body (HTML):
• A high-quality reproduction of a famous historic artwork.
Ready to hang or display, perfect for home, office, gift. Choose your desired size and whether you want it come in a frame  or the print only.
Order a print only, or a framed print.

Print only dimensions:
A5: 15 x 18cm or 5.9 x 7.1 inches
A4: 21 x 30cm or 8.3 x11.7 inches
A3: 42 x 30cm or 16.5 x 11.7 inches
A2: 42.0 x 59.cm or 16.53 x 23.39 inches
A1: 59.4 x 84cm or 23.39 x 33.11 inches.

Framed Print, Exterior Frame dimensions:
A5: 18 x 24cm or 7x10 inches
A4: 24 x 33cm or 10x13 inches
A3: 33 x 45cm or 13x17 inches
A2: 45 x 62cm or 17x24 inches
A1: 62 x 87cm or 24x36 inches



• Poster prints: Professionally & sympathetically created to show off their original vibrant colours

• Poster prints: Made with specialized 230 gsm poster paper which has been optimized for traditional images. Canon Lucia pigment ink which gives bright, vibrant images which when stored under the right condition will not fade for 200 years. The Poster prints have a small white border/margin around the edge of the paper, to preserve the entire original image. The Poster prints have a small white paper around the image area, preserving the entire original picture and keeping the original aspect ratio within the standard paper size. This ensures the picture is perfect on its own or for any standard frame size.

• Frames: Stylish, modern High quality Fiberboard and British made with a black or white wood effect. Frames are ready to hang with built in hooks in the back. A4 and A5 frames have a retractable back flap and so can also stand on a flat surface.

• Frames: Glazing - 2 mm cast acrylic with optical clarity ensures your artwork is displayed at its best. Potential damage from sunlight is greatly reduced by UV protection. It's also much safer than glass in your home or workplace and being 100% recyclable, it's great for the environment too.

• All items dispatched day of ordering or next working day and should be with you in 2-3 days in the UK, 1-2 weeks for international orders. (Excluding weekends & bank holidays etc)

• Posters are sent in a tube or a hardback envelope. Framed Pictures are sent bubble wrapped in a hard box.

• Bullet Proof, No Quibble guarantee! You can return anything we send you up to 60 days after you receive it. In the unlikely event you are not completely satisfied we will give you a full refund and send you a label to return the package. If you have any issues, kindly contact us first and we will do everything to solve any problem to your satisfaction.
